{"tid":2212304,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(果籽奇趣)有人的地方就有雞！全球逾190億隻雞 雞更是恐龍現存的後代","createTime":"2020-09-21T16:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T17:14:01.000Z","uid":2889,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe22841a8c548cd9dba6527cc99d1b92d871309","tid":2212304,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"全球有超過190億隻雞，牠們的數量是人類的三倍。現時全球家雞的品種就超過500種，除了梵帝岡及南極洲沒有雞以外，雞，全球都有雞！<br />\n<br />\n雞的祖先是紅原雞，牠們原產於亞洲南部，即印度、印尼、中國等地。紅原雞被人類馴化圈養來報時及作為食物，慢慢轉化成現時的家雞。由於飼養牠們需要的空間及食糧少，人們習慣遠行時也會攜帶雞，沿路作為食糧。於是雞就跟隨人類走遍全球，至到17世紀，有人的地方就有雞。<br />\n<br />\n#果籽 #雞 #全部都係雞 #紅原雞 #StayHome #WithMe #跟我一樣 #宅在家<br />\n影片來源:Youtube 果籽 Appledaily<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8ccuAcprEBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8ccuAcprEBQ&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=c78db53d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8ccuAcprEBQ</a>"},{"pid":"c163e5ff7d583c856a9f5cacfd5072ab6e0a5fcc","tid":2212304,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"又係怪奇剪片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9095095f57ad0d9de3d2b3c91d535c9d960c398e","tid":2212304,"uid":144126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c163e5ff7d583c856a9f5cacfd5072ab6e0a5fcc","tid":2212304,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"又係怪奇剪片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"蘋果可唔可以揾集專訪佢<br />\n問吓每次隊咗幾多草先剪到啲咁高質嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5368bda5ea4c4dd711d5714e622b4e691b6ca0","tid":2212304,"uid":116547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}